  "detailed_description": "<strong>《烈山海贰》</strong>是《烈山海》系列的第二部，本部的主题为<strong>“自我找寻”</strong>。<br><br>玩家扮演一名身世成谜的现代少年楚鸿云，因为上古神器昆仑镜的召唤，穿越到了人、神、兽共存的山海境当中。在各族的纷争中，不断做出自己的抉择，并最终找寻到真正的自己的故事。<br><br>游戏将根据玩家的各种选择，<strong>提供多种完全不同的结局</strong>。最终是成为在异界逍遥快活的情圣，还是统治一方的受人尊敬的帝王，还是为了复仇弑杀成性的天地共主，都将由你自己决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/1c9da918dfac38ddd45a36cfaf47dfd4.avif?t=1708875572\" width=800 height=92 /></span><br><br>您可以通过多种方式联系到我们，不管是谈游戏、报bug、还是找攻略，找福利，我们都全方位各种欢迎您~<br><br><strong>1、玩家QQ群：</strong>704839701<br><br><strong>[2、官方百度贴吧：[/b]烈山海吧<br><br><strong>3、官方B站号码：</strong>图纳密游戏<br><br><strong>4、官方微博：</strong>烈山海官方微博<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/fc607dd97ff996d472ad9b9618ec2bb3.avif?t=1708875572\" width=800 height=92 /></span><br><br><strong>1-曲折的主线剧情以及丰富的支线剧情。</strong><br><br>游戏中，可攻略的女性角色多达10余人，在你不同的选择下，她们有可能与你温柔缠绵共枕，也有可能就此撒手人寰，这些都在你的一念之间。<br><br><strong>2-更自由化、更独立的游戏感受</strong>。<br><br>通过主线和支线的丰富剧情选择，玩家可以最终决定的故事结局。<br><br><strong>3-更爽快、自由的战斗。</strong><br><br>各种战斗技能由你任意搭配，多种技能升级体系、神剑养成体系，让战斗更为丰富。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/be0e087764abe0b9ec7a095c59e4cfac.poster.avif?t=1708875572\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/be0e087764abe0b9ec7a095c59e4cfac.webm?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/be0e087764abe0b9ec7a095c59e4cfac.mp4?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/330616c93942d40a182033033ee8bee3.poster.avif?t=1708875572\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/330616c93942d40a182033033ee8bee3.webm?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/330616c93942d40a182033033ee8bee3.mp4?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4-丰富的奇遇和小游戏玩法。</strong><br><br>在游戏中结实填海的精卫、帮助治水的大禹，以及正在尝百草的神农。让你在一个游戏中就可以体会到多种游戏玩法，快乐多多。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/c7e9539dd3d58d4fd82ce0bc33c31fe2.poster.avif?t=1708875572\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/c7e9539dd3d58d4fd82ce0bc33c31fe2.webm?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705220/extras/c7e9539dd3d58d4fd82ce0bc33c31fe2.mp4?t=1708875572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
